{"tid":2023383,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"真係on9仔先唔理屎家軍","createTime":"2020-05-19T03:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T06:41:54.000Z","uid":16406,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5c5a260f0f08e608d5c802a3f9df202f724ea4","tid":2023383,"uid":16406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:32:11.000Z","msg":"利申左先 一個都無睇開屎家軍啲片<br />\n<br />\n明眼人都睇得出而家係政府控制屎家軍既第一步<br />\n當政府既錢圈養住佢地 等佢地經濟上慢慢咁依賴上政府 最後政府叫佢做咩就做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那太多呢啲類似招數<br />\n自由行 一帶一路等等 好大程度都係令其他人對自己更大程度既依賴 最後就奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地可以壟斷哂成個YouTube 既輿論<br />\n今日可以話留意返聲援手足<br />\n第日叫人撐政府都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然兒燈係無人睇佢 但好多10幾歲細路都有睇佢地 影響緊既係下一代<br />\n<br />\n今日佢地可以係黃<br />\n聽日都可能係<br />\n但後日呢？我就唔知了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a7991310a4b2dc763f97ba3d65b4a7f8c04fbc","tid":2023383,"uid":90425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"屎圍爐打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d637bc1a23f4648c3cfbb7311dafcc90521765","tid":2023383,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"咩係屎家軍"},{"pid":"76d1dfb840802f1d4b0a043410d35cc258fa02b4","tid":2023383,"uid":89066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"佢地又&rdquo;黃&rdquo;又搵咁多 唔駛我地啦 <br />\n不過關心下D 又黃又無人理嘅手足YouTuber 好過"},{"pid":"71c23e3f4a81fa6f93c9a40a0ae38b86dfbeb71c","tid":2023383,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78d637bc1a23f4648c3cfbb7311dafcc90521765","tid":2023383,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"咩係屎家軍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:37:09.0